  <summary date="2022-03-04T16:18:14Z" status="Introduced in House">Say No to Indoctrination Act

This bill prohibits the use of federal funds to teach or advance concepts that separate individuals based on race, color, or national origin; assign characteristics to individuals based on race, color, or national origin; or imply that the United States is an inherently racist country.</summary>
